OL,3,CTrial date set for man accused of
OL,4,Cmurdering a grandfather outside pub
OL,6,FA trial date has been set for the man
OL,7,Fcharged with murdering a grandfather
OL,8,Fafter punching him outside a village
OL,9,Fpub.
OL,11,FDavid Darke, 66, suffered a serious
OL,12,Fhead injury outside the Crown Inn in
OL,13,FAppleby Magna, Leicestershire, on
OL,14,FSunday, 21 December. He died in
OL,15,Fhospital a week later.
OL,17,FNathan Gothard, 36, who has been
OL,18,Fcharged with murder, appeared at
OL,19,FLeicester Crown Court on Wednesday,
OL,20,Fvia video link from HMP Leicester.
