OL,6,FWearing a grey tracksuit, Gothard, of
OL,7,FChurch Street, Appleby Magna, spoke
OL,8,Fonly to confirm his name and that he
OL,9,Fcould hear the judge during the nine-
OL,10,Fminute hearing.
OL,12,FGothard was told he would have to
OL,13,Fappear in court on 26 January to enter
OL,14,Fa plea. A provisional date for a seven-
OL,15,Fday trial was set for April 27.
OL,17,FJudge Lucking said: "The defendant
OL,18,Fwill be remanded into custody. A trial
OL,19,Fis to be listed, time estimate seven
OL,20,Fdays."
