OL,6,FShe said the jury would have a second
OL,7,Fweek, and potentially a third, for
OL,8,Fdeliberations.
OL,10,FMr Darke's family had paid tribute in
OL,11,Fa statement released through
OL,12,FLeicestershire Police: "Dave was a
OL,13,Fdeeply loved father to three daughters
OL,14,Fand a proud grandfather to three boys.
OL,16,F"He was a much-loved brother and a
OL,17,Fdear friend. Dave will live on forever
OL,18,Fin our hearts, minds and souls.
